name: Team Flight Tactics
desc: TFT is a round-based strategy game that pits you against seven oppoonents in a free-for-all race to build a powerful team that fights on your behalf. There are so many comps for thsi game mode. So far right now, E-girls comp is super strong. Feel free to try this comp and rank up.

name: Dark Star Comp
desc: Dark Star comp is super strong. Jhin gets high damage and this comp is unbeatable.
